              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The 242Pu targets were produced by molecular deposition",
                "from isopropanol solutions.Target backings were",
                "composed of 99.995% pure Ti foils with thickness",
                "of (2.2 +- 0.4) mu-m. Five target stacks composed of a",
                "2 mu-m natNi foil, a 25.4 mu-m Al foil containment",
                "envelope, and the 242PuO2 target deposited on Ti foil",
                "were used. 242Pu target thickness was between",
                "150-500 mu-g/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
